article_title: New pier, seawall nearing completion at Calf Pasture Beach
article_text:
Norwalk, CT (06855)

Today

Sunshine to start, then a few afternoon clouds. High near 85F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy early followed by cloudy skies overnight. Slight chance of a rain shower. Low 59F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph.

og.description: NORWALK -- A year and a half after Hurricane Sandy devastated Calf Pasture Beach, a new seawall and jetty are in place and a stronger, sturdier fishing pier is nearing
